# Personal job-search data — never commit real data to this repo.
JobSearch/data/jobs.json
JobSearch/data/jobs.backup.json
JobSearch/artifact/board.html

# Per-job context drop folder (keep the README, ignore everything a user drops in)
JobSearch/context/*
!JobSearch/context/README.md

# Tailored application documents (keep the README, ignore real PDFs/folders)
Applications/*
!Applications/README.md

# Filled-in personal profile (only the .template.md versions are tracked)
Profile/master-profile.md
Profile/preferences.md
Profile/github-projects.md
Profile/feedback-log.md

# OS / editor / Python cruft
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
